Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到魔法之国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,莎利欧 莎利欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出双手就会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,属于你的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctu Orfei
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aude Fraetor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,658)}Shiny Arc
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,闪光之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,记住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,坚信不疑的心就是你的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,终于来到圣地了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,世界第一魔女 闪光的莎利欧曾经学习过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在这里成为魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(535,658)}Luna Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,请问去新月学园的公交站在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,闪光的莎利欧就读过的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,知道去新月学园的公交站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这附近应该有个公交站的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这个镇上没有公交站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,地图上明明有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,话说这个地图也太简略了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,画成这样谁看得懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,找到啦 找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是新月学园的新生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正要去开学典礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点害怕一个人去魔女学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,六岁时看过闪光的莎利欧的魔法表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,之后就梦想成为一名魔女了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说是超越梦想的宿命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定知道的吧 闪光的莎利欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看 莎利欧的稀有卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,莎利欧在魔法界也是数一数二的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可我身边一个喜欢莎利欧的小伙伴都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,老是被说「你在说什么年代的事啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,除了莎利欧外没人能做到那么厉害的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她可是把月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,傀儡魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次亲眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,乖 乖 来姐姐这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕的 不怕不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊 我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么做到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也从网购的魔法教材里学了一点 但是完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还不知道能不能施展基础魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,希望入学后就能用莎利欧那样的魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,走开 走开 走开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 那家伙搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,新月学园的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,春假怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不管去哪都是游客 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,听说参加今天开学典礼的新生中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个不是魔法世家出身的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 最近学校放太多普通人进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,据说最近学校经营紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不招些非魔法世家出身的人就经营不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,新月学园的品位都被拉低了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可能连扫帚都不会骑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,新月学园历史上还没有一个魔女不会骑扫帚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,篝…篝亚津子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,新生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,希望公交能早点到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,公交？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 这里不是公交站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是什么都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这里会来公交吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是为扫帚准备的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,658)}Ley Line Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,灵脉传送站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这里和新月学园由灵脉相连接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法能量自太古时代开始就奔腾在灵脉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,借着这股魔力就可以飞到新月学园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是魔法高速公路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是魔女基本常识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是开学典礼迟到了 就要被魔法界永远放逐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈和雅尼让我带太多礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia F…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,开学典礼马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没见过你 新生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,新月学园的校规很严格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,迟到了就进不了学校了 会被立马退学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有扫帚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就算有我也不会骑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉 我要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没试过两个人一起骑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定试一试就能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到魔女里还有如此亲切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫篝亚津子 叫我亚子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫洛蒂 赶紧上来吧 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,起飞吧 我的扫帚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 飞起来了 飞起来了 飞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,行李好像太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,打开吧 前往新月学园的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 怎么回事 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了 放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖坐好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,行李…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(970,658)}Forest of Arcturus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一般的魔女无法进入传说中的大角星森林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况还是第一次碰到 太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你带着盐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,盐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,灵脉讨厌含盐的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,梅干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,扔了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有梅干我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 快扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(725,658)}Alcor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 阿尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,难道在大角星森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 宝物平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,死…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦至极说的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还…还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女没那么容易死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事 扫帚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看来到目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,目的地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说这里就是新月学园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,开学典礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 这里是不认识的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大角星森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大角星…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 禁断之森？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,古老传说中的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是被魔法之树保护着的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦迷路了 就算是魔女也很难出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 那就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要赶不上开学典礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别说赶不上了 可能一辈子都出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你别吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,找到掉下来的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,亚子 快离开！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么鬼东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(535,658)}Mandrake
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,曼德拉草 食人植物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,两位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿站好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Juras Haras Haras
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,念咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,咒文？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就能找到出去的路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Kate…Fla FlaFla？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,腹部用力 声音再大点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么东西 刚才的咒文是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,「混蛋 不服就把我吃了」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(1020,658)}Cockatrice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只能在大角星森林找到的传说中的鸡蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,据说羽毛上有剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对于剧毒收藏家来说是非常稀有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来吸引它的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我会趁机把羽毛拔下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 你把我们当诱饵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 是祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再念一遍刚才的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼才念！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对对 当心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是碰到它的气息 你们会变成石头的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,停停停停…停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要赶紧逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再磨蹭下去就赶不上开学典礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这下完了 肯定赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要成为魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只要伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,故事一定会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,心跳不已的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,充满期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,属于我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是… 莎利欧的魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂 快躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼 看过来 冲我拍手的方向来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,苏西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,苏西·曼芭芭拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 苏西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,三个人一起骑没法逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这次喷火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她们为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,658)}Shiny Rod
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,闪光魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,烫烫烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,吟诵言之叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快念咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,魔杖…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctu Orfei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctu Orfei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aude
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aude
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraetor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,闪光之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的假期是如何度过的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这所历史悠久的魔女学校培育出了众多杰出的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们须从今天开始带着自豪与冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,且不忘谦逊与虚心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里专心钻研魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 开学典礼现在开…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一场闻所未闻的开学典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是校长特别允许才能入学的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可不要忘了这份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来跟室友打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始的三年时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,学校会特别对你们三人进行严苛的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫篝亚津子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
